地震发生后，四川、甘肃、陕西等地震灾区治安形势总体平稳，[[中国公安部|中国公安部]]指挥中心未接报重大刑事案件、群死群伤的火灾、交通事故<ref>{{cite web| language =zh-hans| publisher =中央政府门户网站| title =公安部：四川汶川地震灾区社会治安形势总体平稳| url =http://www.gov.cn/gzdt/2008-05/13/content_971084.htm| author =中国公安部| date =2008-05-13| accessdate =2010-06-06| deadurl =no| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140223022137/http://www.gov.cn/gzdt/2008-05/13/content_971084.htm| archivedate =2014-02-23}}</ref>。不过因为地震损害严重，灾区部分災民搶掠救援物資及商店<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = [[人民网|人民网]]（转自 《健康时报》） | title = 公安特警在北川灾区抓获28名趁火打劫的犯罪嫌疑人 | url = http://society.people.com.cn/GB/8217/122500/122647/7255355.html | author = 赵安平、刘桥斌 | date = 2008-05-18 | accessdate = 2010-05-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111208160517/http://society.people.com.cn/GB/8217/122500/122647/7255355.html | archivedate = 2011-12-08 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web| language =zh-hans| publisher =[[搜狐|搜狐]]（转自中国西部网）| title =震灾中趁火打劫 无德导游盗走网吧营业款| url =http://travel.sohu.com/20080518/n256931424.shtml| author =李妍| date =2008-05-18| accessdate =2010-05-30| deadurl =no| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20121121024146/http://travel.sohu.com/20080518/n256931424.shtml| archivedate =2012-11-21}}</ref>，也有災民在搶掠過程起爭執而打鬥，或搶掠物資再出售圖利<ref>{{cite web| language =zh-hant| publisher =香港《太陽報》| title =醜陋的國民，卑鄙的行徑，救災物資被搶無人管| url =http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/news/20080518/20080518023053_0000.html| author =李向榮| date =2008-05-18| accessdate =2010-05-30| deadurl =no| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20090607081025/http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/news/20080518/20080518023053_0000.html| archivedate =2009-06-07}}</ref>；亦有黑心商人伺机抬高物價<ref>{{cite web| language =zh-hant| publisher =香港《太陽報》| title =趁災搶劫無處不在| url =http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/news/20080523/20080523024305_0000.html| author =| date =2008-05-23| accessdate =2010-05-30| deadurl =no| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20110615061347/http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/news/20080523/20080523024305_0000.html| archivedate =2011-06-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| language =zh-hant| publisher =香港《太陽報》| title =無良商人抬高物價| url =http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/news/20080530/20080530025729_0000.html| author =| date =2008-05-30| accessdate =2010-05-30| deadurl =no| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20080601232759/http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/news/20080530/20080530025729_0000.html| archivedate =2008-06-01}}</ref>。此外，警方偵破一些诈骗案件<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = 网易（转自中国新闻网） | title = 2男子建网站借地震赈灾为名网上诈骗被抓 | url = http://news.163.com/08/0519/04/4C9EU09Q00011229.html | author = 丁梅、赵家新 | date = 2008-05-19 | accessdate = 2010-05-30 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140222043615/http://news.163.com/08/0519/04/4C9EU09Q00011229.html | archivedate = 2014-02-22 }}</ref>，包括部分[[黑客|黑客]]入侵部分[[中國紅十字會|中國紅十字會]]网站篡改捐款账号<ref>{{cite web| language =zh-hans| publisher =网易（转自《现代金报》）| title =黑客入侵红十字会官网篡改募捐帐号| url =http://tech.163.com/08/0517/10/4C4U7KJQ000915BF.html| author =吴双颖| date =2008-05-17| accessdate =2010-05-30| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20080724004812/http://tech.163.com/08/0517/10/4C4U7KJQ000915BF.html| archivedate =2008-07-24}}</ref>；或谎称求助，进行短信诈骗<ref>{{cite web | language=zh-hans | publisher = 中国新闻网（《新闻晨报》） | title = 上海警方抓获8名借赈灾短信诈骗分子 | url = http://www.chinanews.com.cn/sh/news/2008/05-16/1251936.shtml | author = 罗剑华 | date = 2008-05-16 | accessdate = 2010-05-30 }}</ref>。而在灾区，有人口販子到災區拐賣嬰兒<ref>{{cite web |language=zh-hans |publisher=[[联合早报|联合早报]]（转自《新明日报》） |title=灾区贩卖幼婴 6人被捕 |url=http://www.zaobao.com/special/newspapers/2008/05/xmrb080525f.shtml |author= |date=2008-05-25 |accessdate=2010-05-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080527225547/http://www.zaobao.com/special/newspapers/2008/05/xmrb080525f.shtml |archivedate=2008-05-27 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |language=zh-hant |publisher=新浪香港（转自《星岛日报》） |title=江油市拘六拐賣犯救五嬰 |url=http://news.sina.com.hk/cgi-bin/nw/show.cgi/32/1/1/749491/1.html |author= |date=2008-05-25 |accessdate=2010-05-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080527073457/http://news.sina.com.hk/cgi-bin/nw/show.cgi/32/1/1/749491/1.html |archivedate=2008-05-27 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>、有無良商人將劣質的[[黑心棉|黑心棉]]製成棉被并将其賣到災區醫院<ref>{{cite web| language =zh-hans| publisher =新浪网（转自中国新闻网）| title =质检总局：四川在救灾物资中发现黑心棉制品| url =http://dailynews.sina.com/gb/chn/chnpolitics/chinanews/file/20080529/0100456271.html| author =| date =2008-05-29| accessdate =2010-05-30| deadurl =no| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140222130546/http://dailynews.sina.com/gb/chn/chnpolitics/chinanews/file/20080529/0100456271.html| archivedate =2014-02-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| language =zh-hant| publisher =香港《太阳报》| title =「黑心棉」賣醫院| url =http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/news/20080530/20080530030224_0000.html| author =| date =2008-05-30| accessdate =2010-05-30| deadurl =no| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20080920083913/http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/news/20080530/20080530030224_0000.html| archivedate =2008-09-20}}</ref>。

2008年5月21日，四川地震重災區[[德陽市|德陽市]]發生大規模騷亂，數千憤怒的民眾懷疑有人侵吞轉賣賑災物資而進行抗議，最後演變成流血衝突<ref>{{cite web |language=zh-hant |publisher=新浪网（转自《明报》） |title=物資疑遭侵吞惹騷亂 |url=http://news.sina.com.hk/cgi-bin/nw/show.cgi/2/1/1/746567/1.html |author=梁曙光、覃純健、秦偉、林迎、李紹昌 |date=2008-05-23 |accessdate=2010-05-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101017122853/http://news.sina.com.hk/cgi-bin/nw/show.cgi/2/1/1/746567/1.html |archivedate=2010-10-17 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。而灾区亦出现言论冲突，比如优先撤离台湾人引发受困九寨沟九黄机场的其他旅客不满，有旅客拦住登机舱口，双方引发冲突<ref>{{cite web| language =zh-hant| publisher =中国评论新闻| title =愛心噴發 政治讓位| url =http://www.chinareviewnews.com/doc/1006/8/4/0/100684083.html?coluid=33&kindid=1671&docid=100684083&mdate=0630145023| author =蔡逸儒| date =2008-06-30| accessdate =2010-05-30| deadurl =no| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20150923221903/http://www.chinareviewnews.com/doc/1006/8/4/0/100684083.html?coluid=33&kindid=1671&docid=100684083&mdate=0630145023| archivedate =2015-09-23}}</ref>。此外，《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》等媒体报道有大量孕妇在震后[[流产|流产]]，居民怀疑流产是临时居住屋的建材中[[甲醛|甲醛]]超标所引起，四川当地政府也禁止媒体报道相关事件<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/05/06/world/asia/06quake.html|title=Year After China Quake, New Births, Old Wounds|publisher=《纽约时报》|date=2009-05-05|author=EDWARD WONG|accessdate=2010-05-29|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120825195535/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/05/06/world/asia/06quake.html|archivedate=2012-08-25}}</ref>。而这一事件也导致[[台湾|台湾]][[八八水灾|八八水灾]]中[[佳冬乡|佳冬乡]]的居民、乡长质疑中国大陆捐助的组合屋的品質问题，一度表示拒收<ref>{{cite web|language=zh-hans|url=http://gb.nownews.com:6060/2009/08/19/11490-2493795.htm|title=陆捐汇编屋含过高甲醛？佳冬乡拒收！|publisher=NOWnews（转自东森新闻）|date=2009-08-09|accessdate=2010-05-29}}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

=== 心理 ===
尽管地震发生后的救援行动中出现的譬如“[[可乐男孩|可乐男孩]]”、“[[猪坚强|猪坚强]]”等事迹反映了灾区民众的坚强与乐观一面，然而更多的心理问题与自杀案件反映出地震后的负面影响。2008年10月3日，因丧子之痛加上高度工作压力，北川县农办主任[[董玉飞|董玉飞]]在自己寓所内自杀<ref>{{cite web| language =zh-hans| publisher =新华网| title =北川官员震后自杀 心理和工作压力是主因| url =http://news.xinhuanet.com/video/2008-10/29/content_10272988.htm| author =新华网| date =2008-10-29| accessdate =2010-06-06| deadurl =no| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20100615052021/http://news.xinhuanet.com/video/2008-10/29/content_10272988.htm| archivedate =2010-06-15}}</ref>；2009年4月20日，北川县宣传部副部长[[冯翔_(北川)|冯翔]]在寓所自杀<ref>{{cite web| language =zh-hans| publisher =中国广播网（转自齐鲁日报）| title =自杀干部冯翔的多面人生| url =http://www.cnr.cn/gundong/200904/t20090422_505310568.html| author =杨珂、张跃伟| date =2009-04-22| accessdate =2010-06-06| deadurl =no| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20150319052916/http://www.cnr.cn/gundong/200904/t20090422_505310568.html| archivedate =2015-03-19}}</ref>。此外，[[都江堰市|都江堰市]]、[[安县|安县]]、[[绵阳市|绵阳市]]、[[平武县|平武县]]等接连发生民众自杀<ref>{{cite web| language =zh-hans| publisher =世界娱乐报道| title =不止北川冯翔董玉飞 十大汶川地震灾区跳楼自缢事件盘点| url =http://ent.icxo.com/htmlnews/2009/04/21/1353855_1.htm| author =| date =2009-04-21| accessdate =2010-06-06| deadurl =no| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20091230113058/http://ent.icxo.com/htmlnews/2009/04/21/1353855_1.htm| archivedate =2009-12-30}}</ref>，这些事件引起民间及官方对于灾后心理干预及援助重视及行动<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = 搜狐网（转自CCTV） | title = 央视反思北川干部自杀 灾区干部心理健康引关注 | url = http://news.sohu.com/20090422/n263539005.shtml | author =  | date = 2009-04-22 | accessdate = 2010-06-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110919215423/http://news.sohu.com/20090422/n263539005.shtml | archivedate = 2011-09-19 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = 河北新闻网（转自《南方都市报》） | title = 汶川2.0：看不见的重建是缓慢的 | url = http://ping.hebnews.cn/zhpl/2010/0513/ff808081288ab5b801288d8ccdf610f9.html | author = 吴珊 | date = 2010-05-13 | accessdate = 2010-06-06 }}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | language = zh-hans | author = 伍新春、侯志瑾、臧伟伟、张宇迪、常雪亮 | title = 汶川地震极重灾区中小学校的心理援助现状与需求——以茂县、汶川县和都江堰市为例 | url = http://www.cnki.com.cn/Article/CJFDTotal-HNSB200903025.htm | journal = 《华南师范大学学报（社会科学版）》 | volume = 3 | issue =  | pages = 110-114 | year = 2009 | id = 6 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140305054114/http://www.cnki.com.cn/Article/CJFDTotal-HNSB200903025.htm | archivedate = 2014-03-05 | access-date = 2014-03-01 }}</ref>。

