汶川地震后，中国公民张晓辉起诉地震局发布虚假信息、隐瞒地震预测，而因非具体行政行为为由被拒绝受理<ref>{{cite web |language=zh-hans |url=http://www1.voanews.com/chinese/news/china/CHINA-EARTH-QUAKE-20091126-74763557.html |title=中国公民起诉地震局发布虚假信息被拒 |work=美国之音 |date=2009-11-26 |accessdate=2010-02-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091130165405/http://www1.voanews.com/chinese/news/china/CHINA-EARTH-QUAKE-20091126-74763557.html |archivedate=2009-11-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。此外，异见人士[[黃琦|黃琦]]由于幫助四川大地震死難者家長调查<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hant | publisher = BBC中文网 | title = 黃琦案成都審結法院擇日宣判 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/chinese/trad/hi/newsid_8180000/newsid_8184700/8184725.stm | author =  | date = 2009-08-05 | accessdate = 2010-05-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090808213431/http://news.bbc.co.uk/chinese/trad/hi/newsid_8180000/newsid_8184700/8184725.stm | archivedate = 2009-08-08 }}</ref>，于2009年11月23日被法院以“[[非法持有国家机密文件罪|非法持有国家机密文件罪]]”宣判，判处有期徒刑三年<ref>{{cite web| language =zh-hans| publisher =联合早报| title =调查川震豆腐渣工程 黄琦被判监三年| url =http://chinese.irib.ir/news/reports/item/14164-%E8%B0%83%E6%9F%A5%E5%B7%9D%E9%9C%87%E8%B1%86%E8%85%90%E6%B8%A3%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B-%E9%BB%84%E7%90%A6%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%A4%E7%9B%91%E4%B8%89%E5%B9%B4| author =| date =2009-11-24| accessdate =2014-05-12| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140513021247/http://chinese.irib.ir/news/reports/item/14164-%E8%B0%83%E6%9F%A5%E5%B7%9D%E9%9C%87%E8%B1%86%E8%85%90%E6%B8%A3%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B-%E9%BB%84%E7%90%A6%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%A4%E7%9B%91%E4%B8%89%E5%B9%B4| archivedate =2014-05-13}}</ref>。而[[南京师范大学|南京师范大学]]副教授[[郭泉|郭泉]]撰文批評四川災區學校「豆腐渣工程」﹐亦被控「[[顛覆國家政權罪|顛覆國家政權罪]]」<ref>{{cite web |language=zh-hans |publisher=VOA |title=郭泉教授颠覆国家政权？ |url=http://www1.voanews.com/chinese/news/GUOQUAN-CHINA_20091017-64664147.html |author=申华 |date=2009-10-17 |accessdate=2010-05-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100402094734/http://www1.voanews.com/chinese/news/GUOQUAN-CHINA_20091017-64664147.html |archivedate=2010-04-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，被判处有期徒刑十年<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = RFA自由亚洲电台 | title = 郭泉被以颠覆国家政权罪刑事拘留 | url = http://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/guoquan-11132008094552.html | author = 严修 | date = 2008-11-13 | accessdate = 2010-05-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090624014019/http://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/guoquan-11132008094552.html | archivedate = 2009-06-24 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web| language =zh-hans| publisher =苹果日报| title =揭四川豆腐渣工程被控郭泉否認顛覆國家| url =http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20090808/13075529| author =| date =2009-12-17| accessdate =2014-05-12| deadurl =no| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140512214902/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20090808/13075529| archivedate =2014-05-12}}</ref>。另外，四川作家[[譚作人|譚作人]]（属于争议人物，后因牵扯天安门六四事件而被判入狱，于2014年刑满释放）亦在汶川地震後致力於調查災區學校豆腐渣工程，並搜集川震遇難學生名單。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rfi.fr/actucn/articles/112/article_12971.asp|title=谭作人的《5·12学生档案》倡议书|publisher=RFI|date=2009年4月3日|accessdate=2009年4月11日|archive-date=2009年4月6日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090406171222/http://www.rfi.fr/actucn/articles/112/article_12971.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外，原定于2010年3月1日在成都举行的民间问责中国地震局研讨会，其会场被警方毁坏<ref>{{cite web|language=zh-hans|url=http://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/dizhen-03012010095407.html|title=地震问责研讨会被公安禁 主办者被软禁器材被查抄|work=自由亚洲电台|date=2010-03-01|accessdate=2010-03-02|author=乔龙|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100519033230/http://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/dizhen-03012010095407.html|archivedate=2010-05-19}}</ref>。

== 救援 ==
[[Image:R0013449.JPG|left]]
{{Main|汶川大地震各方反應}}
由于地震发生突然、加之通往震中等地的交通堵塞，当地政府及民众首先采取一定的抗震自救行动<ref>{{cite web| language =zh-hans| publisher =《四川新闻网》| title =汶川县漩口中学抗震自救纪实| url =http://local.newssc.org/system/20080605/000004898.htm| author =| date =2008-06-05| accessdate =2014-05-12| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140512224835/http://local.newssc.org/system/20080605/000004898.htm| archivedate =2014-05-12}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| language =zh-hans| publisher =新浪网（转自巴中网）| title =四川地震组图:都江堰灾区群众抗灾自救| url =http://news.sina.com.cn/c/p/2008-05-15/145215546255.shtml| author =| date =2008-05-23| accessdate =2014-05-06| deadurl =no| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140512215122/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/p/2008-05-15/145215546255.shtml| archivedate =2014-05-12}}</ref>。地震後，中華人民共和國發動自和平時代以來最龐大的救援行動，派出逾十萬軍人、調動全國各地的救援队伍，亦協調來自全球各地的救援队伍。截至2008年9月25日12时，抢险救灾人员已累计解救和转移1486407人；因地震受伤住院治疗累计96544人，已出院93597人，仍有272人住院，其中四川转外省市伤员仍住院106人，共救治伤病员4305820人次。外地向灾区调运的救灾帐篷共计157.97万顶、被子486.69万床、衣物1410.13万件、燃油414.6万吨、煤炭885.8万吨<ref name="jzz"/>。

=== 政府 ===
{{Wikiquote|温家宝#关于汶川大地震|温家宝关于汶川大地震的讲话}}
在整個救災工作，[[中華人民共和國政府|中華人民共和國中央政府]]一直扮演主導角色，多位最高層領導先後到達災區指挥，公安、交通、電訊、地震、民政各部均被調度管理救災工作。當地震發生1小时27分钟后，[[中國共產黨中央政治局常務委員會|中共中央政治局常委]]、[[中華人民共和國國務院總理|國務院總理]][[温家宝|温家宝]]赶赴灾区，晚上抵達都江堰到指揮中心指揮救援工作<ref>{{cite web| language =zh-hans| publisher =新华网| title =溫家寶總理抵都江堰：步行也要儘快進入受災最嚴重地區| url =http://news.xinhuanet.com/newscenter/2008-05/12/content_8154687.htm| author =李斌| date =2008-05-12| accessdate =2010-05-22| deadurl =no| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20080517043046/http://news.xinhuanet.com/newscenter/2008-05/12/content_8154687.htm| archivedate =2008-05-17}}</ref>，並接連下達救災命令<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = 新华网 | title = 温家寶要求今晚12時前打通通往震中災區的道路 | url = http://news.xinhuanet.com/newscenter/2008-05/13/content_8157163.htm | author = 李斌 | date = 2008-05-13 | accessdate = 2010-05-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080517050744/http://news.xinhuanet.com/newscenter/2008-05/13/content_8157163.htm | archivedate = 2008-05-17 }}</ref>。2008年5月16日，[[中國共產黨中央委員會總書記|中共中央總書記]]、[[中華人民共和國主席|國家主席]]、[[中國共產黨中央軍事委員會主席|中央軍委主席]][[胡錦濤|胡錦濤]]亦飛抵四川視察<ref>{{cite web| language =zh-hans| publisher =新华网| title =胡锦涛在飞机上研究灾情和抗震救灾工作| url =http://news.xinhuanet.com/photo/2008-05/16/content_8184918.htm| author =| date =2008-05-16| accessdate =2010-05-22| deadurl =no| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20080519213221/http://news.xinhuanet.com/photo/2008-05/16/content_8184918.htm| archivedate =2008-05-19}}</ref>。

