b | language = zh-hans | publisher = BBC中文网 | title = 美英领导人去中国使馆吊唁 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/chinese/simp/hi/newsid_7410000/newsid_7411300/7411345.stm | author =  | date = 2008-05-20 | accessdate = 2010-05-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090104062533/http://news.bbc.co.uk/chinese/simp/hi/newsid_7410000/newsid_7411300/7411345.stm | archivedate = 2009-01-04 }}</ref>。[[红十字会与红新月会国际联合会|红十字会与红新月会国际联合会]]驻北京的工作人员[[弗朗西斯·马库斯|弗朗西斯·马库斯]]（{{lang|en|Francis Marcus}}）称赞“中国政府反应迅速有效”，但又说因为灾难规模巨大，“中国政府没办法处理到每个细节。”<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = [[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]] | title = Search for China quake survivors | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/7397489.stm | author =  | date = 2008-05-13 | accessdate = 2010-05-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080515094215/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/7397489.stm | archivedate = 2008-05-15 }}</ref>

